    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>butternut squash cubes </strong>to a heatproof bowl</p><p>Cover the bowl with <strong>cling film</strong> and pierce a few holes in the top</p><p>Put the bowl in the <strong>microwave</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until the butternut squash cubes are fork-tender</p>",
      "order": 2,
