            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>creamed</strong> <strong>coconut </strong>roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the<strong> vegetable stock mix </strong>and the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>creamed</strong> <strong>coconut </strong>in 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your<strong> coconut stock</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse the<strong> green lentils</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
