            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>drained lentils </strong>and <strong>coconut stock</strong> to the pan and cook for 1-2 min further</p><p>Add the <strong>wholemeal pittas </strong>to the<strong> toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until warmed through</p><p>Tip: Alternatively, add them to a baking tray and put them under the grill</p>",
      "order": 5,
