      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>cultured coconut </strong>and <strong>mint sauce</strong> to a bowl and mix it all together – this is your <strong>coconut raita</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>red chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span> </strong>finely</p>",
