      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>warmed pittas</strong> into triangles</p><p>Serve the<strong> butternut squash dal</strong> in bowls with the <strong>coconut raita </strong>and <strong>pitta triangles</strong> to the side</p><p>Tip: Watch out for any cardamom pods!</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chilli rounds </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
